---
description: Tech-stack version gating. Detect exact version from lockfile.
globs: ["package.json","composer.json","package-lock.json","composer.lock"]
alwaysApply: true
---

[FILE] tech-stack.mdc
[OBJ] Version detection and stack loading.
[RULES]
1. [REQ] `[VER-01]` Before loading ANY `tech-stack/` file, read lockfile.
2. [CMD] For PHP: `composer.lock` -> grep package version -> load `tech-stack/<pkg>-<ver>.md`.
3. [CMD] For JS: `package-lock.json` -> grep version -> load `tech-stack/<pkg>-<ver>.md`.
4. [PROHIBIT] NEVER default to v3 for Filament or v11 for Laravel.
5. [REQ] If lockfile missing, use `composer.json`/`package.json` constraints.
6. [REQ] Load `spec.md` from project root if exists.
